folder constructure:

------code\Fact_Checking                                                                         ***************project
----------------------------.settings                                                            ***************generated by Eclipse, ignore it.
----------------------------com					***************root
---------------------------------_pycache				***************generated by Eclipse, ignore it.
---------------------------------NER_				***************NER package
---------------------------------------stanford-ner.jar 			***************.jar file
---------------------------------------english.all.3class.distsim.crf.ser.gz	***************.gz file
---------------------------------__init__.py				***************root
---------------------------------Fact_Checking[205].xlsx		***************facts content. you can delete/modify/add items in it.
---------------------------------Facts_Check.py			***************programme.   click to run it.
----------------------------.project				***************generated by Eclipse, ignore it.
----------------------------.pydevproject				***************generated by Eclipse, ignore it.


Instraction:

	about run:
		1: click on the programme;
		2: the screen will show: Do you wish to use Google translation? If so, Press 1, otherwise press any keys.
		3: input your chooice.
	about modificate/add/delete statements:
		1: just modify the Fact_Checking[205].xlsx 
Others:
	if not install the google translation then the programme will appear errors, so make sure your machine have install it.
	how to install?
		see the documents on https://cloud.google.com/translate/?hl=EN

